**Television production company (2010–2019)**

This article is about the company active from 2010 until 2019. For the branding label used by [Marvel Studios](/Marvel_Studios), see [Marvel Studios §&#160;Marvel Television](/Marvel_Studios). For other uses, see [Marvel Television (disambiguation)](/Marvel_Television_(disambiguation)).

